ADDITIONAL INFORMATION:

The long-awaited new release from Point of Grace is finally here! I Choose You is Point of Grace's ninth album, but is also an album of firsts beginning with new member Leigh Cappillino. This new creative mix has allowed Point of Grace to reshape and update their sound, while maintaining the catchy, signature pop element from prior releases that fans know and love. I Choose You will appeal to long time followers of Point of Grace as well as a whole new generation of fans.
